        "name": "Person of Interest",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "Sometimes, you need to follow the leads as they come in the middle of an investigation. Choose a creature that you can see who isn't, to your knowledge, tied to any of your current investigations. For the next minute, you can Devise a Stratagem against that creature as a free action.",
